TEXT.P:
Lin Ting, vice director-general of the health department's Center
for Disease Control, reminded those who are involved in raising,
slaughtering or delivering poultry and livestock to get inoculated.

The cocktail party was held to mark the signing of business
contracts worth an estimated US$300 million, including a contract
between Chinese Petroleum Corp. and the Russian Institute of
International Relations on a joint crude oil exploration project;
Taiwan Fertilizer Corp.'s purchase of urea (carbamide) from Russia;
and Ho Tung Chemical Co.'s procurement of crude oil.
